m zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7424793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7424793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 22, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xuh1718876337843.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xuh1718876337843.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xuh1718876337843.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mut1665703016835\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $uppercase\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mut1665703016835___uppercase_300096\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Convert the specified string uppercase.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mut1665703016835__topic_d91241e1_d91242e1_d91243e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__p_d91244e1_d91245e1_d91246e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$uppercase</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"NlsLocale\"</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"classic\"</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__section_w2478ab1b7b5_w2479ab1b7_w2480ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__p_d91247e1_d91248e1_d91249e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">FIELD1 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"nlslocale\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mut1665703016835__topic_d60732e1_d60733e1_d60734e1_d60735e1_d60736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184124e94\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__3\">\n String to convert to uppercase; can be a string, field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, or function that evaluates to a string.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NlsLocale</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__3\">Apply locale-based rules based on the value of\n                        the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span>, as specified by\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">$NLS_LOCALE</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">classic</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mut1665703016835__table_d10100e1_d10101e1_d10102e1__entry__3\">\n Apply one-to-one character conversion according to Unicode definitions.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mut1665703016835__topic_d60737e1_d60738e1_d60739e1_d60740e1_d60741e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184124e193\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__p_d91256e1_d91257e1_d91258e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> converted to uppercase.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mut1665703016835__topic_d60742e1_d60743e1_d60744e1_d60745e1_d60746e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184124e206\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mut1665703016835__topic_d60747e1_d60748e1_d60749e1_d60750e1_d60751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184124e215\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665703016835__p_d91268e1_d91269e1_d91270e1\">The way in which strings are converted depends on the NLS settings in effect. If the second argument is omitted, the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlscase</span> is used to determine case conversion behavior. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xfm1665702676151.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfm1665702676151.html\" title=\"You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing.\">Case Conversion</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mut1665703016835__section_xtk_b5z_2cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184124e234\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$uppercase</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example, if the <code class=\"ph codeph\">nlslocale</code> qualifier is used, the\n               German lowercase <code class=\"ph codeph\">ß</code>, which is a single character, is converted to two\n               characters: <code class=\"ph codeph\">SS</code>. (This is known as case folding.)</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mut1665703016835__pre_zjs_b5z_2cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">FIELD1 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"nlslocale\")\n;Result: FIELD1 = GROSS-GERAU</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If the qualifier is set as <code class=\"ph codeph\">classic</code>, the conversion is\n               on a character-by-character basis:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mut1665703016835__pre_aks_b5z_2cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">FIELD2 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"classic\")\n;Result: FIELD2 = GROß-GERAU</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfm1665702676151.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Case Conversion</a><p>You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lmt1718875974603.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$lowercase</a><p>Convert a string to lowercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbh1665703006270.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uppercase (deprecated)</a><p>Convert the specified string to uppercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rnc1665703005296.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lowercase (deprecated)</a><p>Convert a string to lowercase.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424793\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$uppercase Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 22, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $uppercase Convert the specified string uppercase. $uppercase ( String { , \"NlsLocale\" | \"classic\" } ) Example: FIELD1 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"nlslocale\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String to convert to uppercase; can be a string, field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, or function that evaluates to a string. NlsLocale String Apply locale-based rules based on the value of the $nlslocale , as specified by $nlslocale or $NLS_LOCALE . classic String Apply one-to-one character conversion according to Unicode definitions. Return Values String converted to uppercase. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The way in which strings are converted depends on the NLS settings in effect. If the second argument is omitted, the value of $nlscase is used to determine case conversion behavior. For more information, see Case Conversion . Example: Using $uppercase For example, if the nlslocale qualifier is used, the German lowercase ß , which is a single character, is converted to two characters: SS . (This is known as case folding.) FIELD1 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"nlslocale\") ;Result: FIELD1 = GROSS-GERAU Copy If the qualifier is set as classic , the conversion is on a character-by-character basis: FIELD2 = $uppercase (\" Groß-Gerau\", \"classic\") ;Result: FIELD2 = GROß-GERAU Copy Related Links Case Conversion You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing. $lowercase Convert a string to lowercase. uppercase (deprecated) Convert the specified string to uppercase. lowercase (deprecated) Convert a string to lowercase. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}